To: "Acosta, Alex (USAFLS)" <AAcosta@usa.doj.gov>, 
Subject: Letter received from Epstein's counsel 
Date: Tue, 08 Jul 2008 20:57:56 +0000 
Importance: Normal 
Hi all —  I received one line from Jack Goldberger, which reads: "I am out of the office today. I will response [sic] to your 
fax of July 8, 2008 by return of fax tomorrow." 
EFTA00013557
